---
import "../styles/global.css";
import FAQ from "../components/FAQ.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import SubredditCard from "../components/SubredditCard.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/icon.svg" />
        <link rel="alternate icon" type="image/png" sizes="48x48" href="/icon48.png" />
        <link rel="alternate icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/icon16.png" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
        <title>Welcome to Sharp Tabs</title>
        <meta
            name="description"
            content="Welcome to Sharp Tabs! Learn the most useful shortcuts and get started with the best vertical tabs extension."
        />
    </head>
    <body
        class="relative min-h-screen select-none bg-gradient-to-r from-black via-[#050c18] to-black transition-colors duration-300"
    >
        <Navbar />
        <main class="container mx-auto mt-20 max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 pb-32">
            <h1 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold text-white">Thank you for installing Sharp Tabs!</h1>
            <p class="mb-10 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">
                Please read the following instructions to get the most out of this extension:
            </p>
            <ol class="mb-12 list-inside list-decimal space-y-8 text-gray-300">
                <li>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-white">Sharp Tabs offers the following benefits:</span>
                    <br />
                    Vertical grouped tabs. Type to search tabs. Saving tabs & groups. Auto-organizing tabs.<br />Keyboard
                    shortcuts.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-white">Pin Sharp Tabs to the menu bar:</span>
                    <br />
                    Pin Sharp Tabs to the menu bar to always have it available and access it easily.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-white">Show the popup & search instantly:</span>
                    <br />
                    Assign a keyboard shortcut to open the Sharp Tabs popup and start searching in all windows immediately. You can
                    press the
                    <kbd class="rounded bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 text-sm">Tab</kbd> key to navigate tabs then hit enter to open it.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-white">Modify extension settings:</span>
                    <br />
                    Personalize your experience by adjusting the extension settings to fit your workflow. There's a TON of features
                    already and I will be adding more based on your requests.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-white">Save your session:</span>
                    <br />
                    Make sure to save your session to avoid losing your tabs when your browser crashes. Auto saves are also enabled
                    and run once every 10 minutes.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-white">AI Features (Optional):</span>
                    <br />
                    Want AI-powered tab organization? Get a premium subscription or bring your own free Gemini API key in settings.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-white">Join our community:</span>
                    <br />
                    Connect with other users, share feedback, and stay updated by joining our subreddit below.
                </li>
            </ol>
            <SubredditCard />
        </main>
        <FAQ />
        <div class="h-10"></div>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
